{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_019AxqxNzdJjj8dyGzENBaZG","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_017NofNRX3h1nHsEa8BRTZug","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Lavender Panna Cotta.generated.22.txt","content":"Wiosna | Desery | Dla 6 osób | Przygotowanie 15 min | Chłodzenie 4 godziny\n\nLAVENDER PANNA COTTA\n\nDelicate, silky panna cotta infused with the floral notes of lavender.\nThis sophisticated dessert requires minimal effort but delivers maximum elegance.\nPerfect for special dinners, garden parties, or romantic occasions.\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n- 2 cups heavy cream\n- 1/2 cup whole milk\n- 1/4 cup sugar\n- 1 tbsp dried culinary lavender buds\n- 1 tsp vanilla extract\n- 2 tsp gelatin powder\n- 3 tbsp cold water\n- Honey for drizzling\n- Candied lavender for garnish (optional)\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n1. Combine cream, milk, sugar, and lavender buds in a saucepan.\n2. Heat gently over medium, stirring occasionally, until steaming. Do not boil.\n3. Remove from heat and let steep 30 minutes to infuse.\n4. Strain through a fine mesh sieve, pressing gently on lavender. Discard solids.\n5. Bloom gelatin in cold water for 5 minutes.\n6. Reheat cream mixture gently over low heat.\n7. Whisk in bloomed gelatin until completely dissolved, stirring constantly.\n8. Stir in vanilla extract.\n9. Pour into serving glasses or small ramekins, about 3/4 full.\n10. Chill at least 4 hours until set firm.\n11. Top with honey drizzle and candied lavender. Serve chilled.\n\nMAKE AHEAD:\nCan be prepared up to 2 days in advance. Cover with plastic wrap and refrigerate.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":76912,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":76912},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"31f79979-f917-445a-83c4-99cb8a3cfd6e","uuid":"8f388f6d-feb9-4d16-b596-f5809feefc2b"}
