{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_019AxqxNzdJjj8dyGzENBaZG","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01TrDTXmc8TZRFRGX7jP1NiQ","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Ogórkowa Zupa.generated.22.txt","content":"Lato | Zupy | DLA 4 OSÓB | PRZYGOTOWANIE 15 MIN | GOTOWANIE 20 MIN\n\nOGÓRKOWA ZUPA\n\nOgórkowa zupa, or Polish cucumber soup, is a refreshing summer soup served\neither hot or cold. The dill-infused broth is bright and tangy, perfect for\nwarm days when you want something light yet satisfying and nourishing.\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n- 6 medium cucumbers, peeled and diced\n- 6 cups vegetable or chicken stock\n- 1 large onion, diced\n- 2 tbsp butter\n- 2 cloves garlic, minced\n- 3 tbsp fresh dill, chopped\n- 2 tbsp fresh lemon juice\n- 1/2 cup sour cream\n- 1/4 tsp white pepper\n- Salt to taste\n- Fresh dill sprigs for garnish\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n1. In a large pot, melt butter over medium heat.\n2. Sauté diced onion until translucent, about 5 minutes.\n3. Add minced garlic and cook 1 minute more.\n4. Add diced cucumbers and cook for 3 minutes, stirring occasionally.\n5. Pour in vegetable or chicken stock and bring to a simmer.\n6. Simmer for 15 minutes until cucumbers are tender.\n7. Add fresh dill and lemon juice.\n8. Season with salt and white pepper to taste.\n9. For creamy version, stir in sour cream just before serving.\n10. Serve hot in winter or chill thoroughly and serve cold.\n\nSERVING SUGGESTIONS:\nTop with dollop of sour cream and fresh dill sprig. Serve with dark rye bread.\nCan be made 1 day ahead and stored in refrigerator.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":76912,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":76912},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"31f79979-f917-445a-83c4-99cb8a3cfd6e","uuid":"6aaf523d-a5e3-4a00-920a-70336a3e0a72"}
